data.description: Located in the highly sought after Cambridge on The Lake Community this unit offers a great layout, large room sizes with tons of upside, this is not a unit which you will want to miss!!! The floor plan is ideal with a large living room that offers a bedroom off the living room, this bedroom would be a great home office, add glass french doors to overlook the living room with a very classy feel is just one of the many options this space offers. The formal dining room has a bay like window providing tons of natural sunlight, we have seen other units where they open the kitchen to the dining room/living room with a breakfast bar, again potential here is endless! There is in unit washer/dryer, master suite has a changing room in addition to a great walk in closet and spa like bathroom! This unit is move in ready but has great equity potential for a buyer who wants to complete minor updates. This community offers garage parking, community indoor pool, fitness center and so much more! Do not wait to get inside this unit as units in this complex do not hit the market often!
